Wikipedia was one of the first spaces online where you could learn best stories from Indian Mythology & Folklore. We present stories from cool characters like Tenali Raman and also from folktales like Panchatantra and Katha Sarit Sagar. We also have stories from Indian Mythology which includes Lord Krishna’s stories, stories from Ramayana & Mahabharata and stories of our lovable Gods Ganesha & Shiva.

Enjoy more than 150 stories on KathaKids!
